environmentalDataLogging.entities

Class Project

  • java.lang.Object
    • environmentalDataLogging.entities.BaseEntity
      • environmentalDataLogging.entities.Project

  • @Entity
public class Project
extends BaseEntity
    The Project entity class is the link to the project table in the EnviroDB database. A Project contains all the information relating to a project off the Environmental Technologies lab
